# Build output
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/artifacts/
**/out/
**/dist/
**/build/

# Test and coverage output
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/.coverage/
**/coverage-report/

# Package caches
**/node_modules/
**/.pnpm-store/
**/packages/
**/.nuget/

# Logs and temp files
**/*.log
**/logs/
**/tmp/
**/temp/
**/.tmp/

# OS / editor noise
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.idea/
**/.vs/

# Secrets and local env
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets/
**/*.pfx
**/*.snk
**/*secrets*.json
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

# Generated or heavy assets
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif
**/*.webp
**/*.pdf
**/*.zip
**/*.nupkg

# Research / scratch zones
**/playground/
**/scratch/
**/research-dumps/
**/notes-dump/